Santander Calculates Credit Offered Nueva Rumasa, Expansion Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-02-21T06:46:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/santander-calculates-credit-offered-nueva-rumasa-expansion-says.html
  Banco Santander SA  has begun to
calculate how much credit it has provided for units of Nueva
Rumasa, a holding company controlled by the Ruiz Mateos family,
 Expansion  reported, without citing anyone.  A preliminary estimate shows that Santander gave loans of
140 million euros ($191.5 million) to units of the group, the
newspaper added.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net . 